title: How To Install a K&N Air Intake on a 2015 Subaru WRX 2.0L
description:
See how easy it is to install a K&N air intake on your 2015 Subaru WRX 2.0L. 

K&N 69-8006TTK performance air intake system is easy to install and guaranteed to increase horsepower in 2015 Subaru WRX with a 2.0L engine. When dyno tested, this air intake created an estimated gain of 9.16 horsepower at 4800 RPM.

This air intake includes an oversized washable & reusable air filter that can go up to 100,000 miles between servicing. K&N air intake 69-8006TTK also includes a mandrel bent aluminum intake tube with a black powder-coat finish and heat shield to isolate intake air from engine heat.
tags: K&N Cold Air Intake, CAI, Subaru WRX, how to install, k&n air intake, cold air intake, subaru performance parts, wrx
